          </name>
        </author>
        
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://satyajitpuhan.github.io/or/blog/eic-asia-2026-qcd-hadron-structure/"/>
        <id>https://satyajitpuhan.github.io/or/blog/eic-asia-2026-qcd-hadron-structure/</id>
        
        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;କର୍ମଶାଳା:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; &lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;indico.phys.sinica.edu.tw&#x2F;event&#x2F;495&#x2F;&quot;&gt;EIC-Asia Workshop on QCD and Hadron Structure&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ସ୍ଥାନ:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; Institute of Physics, Academia Sinica, ତାଇପେଇ, ତାଇୱାନ&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ତାରିଖ:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; ଏପ୍ରିଲ ୨୯ – ମେ ୧, ୨୦୨୬&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ମୋଡ୍:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; ବ୍ୟକ୍ତିଗତ ଭାବେ&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ମୁଁ Academia Sinica, ତାଇପେଇରେ ଆୟୋଜିତ &lt;strong&gt;EIC-Asia Workshop on QCD and Hadron Structure&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; ରେ ଭାଗ ନେଲି | ଏହି କର୍ମଶାଳା ଆସନ୍ନ Electron-Ion Collider (EIC) ସମ୍ବନ୍ଧୀୟ ପରୀକ୍ଷା, ଫେନୋମେନୋଲୋଜି ଏବଂ ଲାଟିସ୍ ଗଣନାରେ ବିଶେଷଜ୍ଞମାନଙ୍କୁ ଏକାଠି କରିଥିଲା |&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</summary>
        
